    "fills": "real per-DTE OPRA day-T bars + honest overnight gap + expiry intrinsic settlement (no synthetic mid-life marks) \u2014 inherited byte-for-byte from _dte_expansion_sim.simulate_dte_trade; only the stop check is generalized.",
